r\n<div class=\"hr hr-invisible avia-builder-el-5 el_after_av_textblock el_before_av_textblock \"></div>\r\n<section class=\"av_textblock_section\">\r\n<div class=\"avia_textblock \">\r\n\r\n<strong>3. Specific private notice for children under 18\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\nIt is Pandadar\'sÂ policy to limit the collection of personal information from children to only that which is necessary to obtain parental consent or to participate in a PandadadrÂ program or activity after we have obtained parental consent. Children under 18 years old are not allowed to subscribe or create an account. Only a parent, guardian, or teacher can register the children on the site or give them access to any of PandadarÂ services. As for it, during the registration process, we collect only enough personal information (i.e., parentâs name and email address) necessary to obtain a parentâs permission for his/her child to become a member of Pandadar.\r\n\r\nWe will seek consent from parents for their children to use PandadarÂ services through interview or use of a credit card or other payment verification during the registration process. Parents/teachers will be asked to read the Terms and Conditions and accept them by ticking a box during the registration process. Once registered, children donât have the right to upload personal pictures.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<div class=\"hr hr-invisible avia-builder-el-7 el_after_av_textblock el_before_av_textblock \"></div>\r\n<section class=\"av_textblock_section\">\r\n<div class=\"avia_textblock \">\r\n\r\n<strong>4. General\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\nAlthough every reasonable effort has been made to ensure that all personal information will be so protected, PandadarÂ cannot be responsible for any unauthorised use or misuse of such information and from risks which are inherent in all internet communications.\r\n\r\nPandadarÂ reserves the right to change this Policy with or without notice from time to time.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</section></div>\r\n</div>'